description:
This is a 16 minute workout called 'Physio Neck and Shoulder Stretches GUIDED ROUTINE (15 Mins)' from the channel Michelle Kenway.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Relax and ease neck and shoulder tension with this Physiotherapist guided home stretching exercise routine. Michelle guides you through safe neck stretching exercises that reduce muscle tension and relieve neck and shoulder pain. This stretching routine is the ideal work break at your home desk for relieving stress and neck tension. These stretches are suitable for beginners and intermediate level.

#WithMe  #homeworkout  #neckstretches 
Website: https://www.pelvicexercises.com.au

This 15 minute neck and shoulder stretching routine guides you step by step through a series of gentle stretches for easing neck and shoulder pain and tightness. This routine starts in the sitting position with deep breathing and shoulder mobility exercises. The guided routine progresses through a series of safe stretching and mobility exercises for improving posture and relieving strain on the neck and shoulders.
